snippet.title: The 6-digit computer - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Finally, it's here!
This is the official trailer for out new programming game, The 6-digit Computer. Make programs, read E-Mails, uncover dark secrets and even make your own levels to share with others!
Buy the game here:
https://nnnikki.itch.io/the-6-digit-computer
